{"tid":222370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（賣旗，行善？）樂善堂賣旗要磅旗袋，唔夠秤要繼續賣","createTime":"2017-04-29T13:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T02:36:51.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"746eb052c94abeddd10dd5f54dc29ed89227fab9","tid":222370,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"九龍樂善堂今日舉行全港售旗籌款，為轄下醫療、教育等服務籌募發展經費。有樂善堂王仲銘中學的學生向本報爆料，指學校規定旗袋重量「磅過唔夠秤，要繼續賣」。學生質疑校方做法「做義工啫，做咩要磅？」老師解釋稱這是「獎勵活動」，鼓勵學生積極賣旗。"},{"pid":"5557e938bd1e8b7c1e7b6cb34cc0e029d179147f","tid":222370,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾奶共團體"},{"pid":"96e9390d810c1ab83d61616d5a5401164d219cdf","tid":222370,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170429/large/1493441618_7ffa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170429%2Flarge%2F1493441618_7ffa.jpg&h=073537c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仔軒尼詩道旗站，有老師為學生秤旗袋。("},{"pid":"9f9d32b9bafcb3c2ccfc4df4777a05efb40617ff","tid":222370,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170429/large/1493436855_968b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170429%2Flarge%2F1493436855_968b.jpg&h=b6d074a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n灣仔軒尼詩道旗站，有老師駐守，桌上放有一個手秤。"},{"pid":"398ff501da2c87eb5586d997cb5d0ac78726a6f8","tid":222370,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"逼學生參加埋d on9活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得當年有回條可以選去同唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我tick